Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Death Valley National Park
Description: The hottest place in the world and it is also the lowest point in North America.

Name: Joshua Tree National Park
Description: The two distinct desert ecosystems, the Mojave and the Colorado come together in Joshua Tree National Park.

Name: Orange Coast College
Description: I transferred from Orange Coast College to UCSB, it has the highest transfer rate in CA.

Name: Saipan
Description: It is an island in the Northern Mariana islands featuring a number of villages, plus forests & beaches. I traveled to Saipan in 2013, it is an amazing place to go.

Name: Xi'An
Description: Xi'an is my hometown, once known as Chang'an. One of the famous archaeological sites in Xi'an isTerra Cotta Army.
